name: Dimly Lit
description:
You can find an owl like this in mature, sturdy trees or perhaps in the roof of an old barn. This little night owl has just woken up and she's ready to go find some food. Maybe it'll be a mouse or a vole, but if you get too close she might eat a chunk of you!

Minted for Hen's 500k Objkt celebration.
